    {
      "id": "eScbcPkkIqGghzj5BIN3O",
      "reviewer_label": "Reviewer 1",
      "source": "reviewer_report",
      "round": 1,
      "content_md": "The conclusion asserts that physical activity 'directly lowers' depression risk, but this is an observational cohort and the estimates do not appear adjusted for confounders. Please temper the causal language and report adjusted hazard ratios with 95% confidence intervals. The abstract reports 512 participants while the analysis includes 498; please reconcile and describe attrition. An ethics-approval statement is also missing.",
